author: Janet Eastman | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: Free for the taking? 1902 Colonial Revival house in Johnson Creek flood zone needs to move (photos)
text: If you flip through online real estate sites, you'll see that 2415 SE Ambleside Dr. in Gresham is not for sale. But contact Metro, and you'll find that you can have the 1902 Colonial Revival-style house possibly for free, if you take it away.
